<section class="section showcase-section" id="the-problem">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-top animate-on-scroll">
            <div class="section-label section-label-centered">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg>
                The Problem
            </div>
            <h2 class="section-heading">Social proof is your <span class="serif-italic">secret weapon.</span><br>But most teams never deploy it.</h2>
            <p class="section-desc centered">Buyers need to hear from people like them. But delivering the right proof point, at the right moment, manually — at scale — is impossible.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-grid">
            <div class="problem-card animate-on-scroll">
                <div class="problem-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Reps Don't Know What to Share</h3>
                <p>Your content library has 200 case studies. Your rep has 15 minutes before the call. They guess — or skip it entirely.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="problem-card animate-on-scroll">
                <div class="problem-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Proof Arrives Too Late</h3>
                <p>By the time marketing sends the right case study, the deal has already stalled — or gone to a competitor who was faster.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="problem-card animate-on-scroll">
                <div class="problem-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Peer Conversations Happen Anyway</h3>
                <p>Prospects find their own references through Slack communities and LinkedIn — conversations you can't see, control, or influence.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="problem-card animate-on-scroll">
                <div class="problem-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Marketing Can't Prove Impact</h3>
                <p>You created 40 new case studies this quarter. You have no idea which ones moved deals forward — or if any of them were ever used.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


